    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Keep your nails, lashes, eyebrows, and face looking clean, fresh, and groomed on the go with the ToolTreaux 9pc Deluxe Beauty Tool Kit! Our set comes with 9 basic tools every woman needs to be ready for any occasion on the go in one convenient set - an eyelash curler, eyebrow tweezer, nail brush, nail clippers, emery boards, and blackhead remover tools. Our beauty scrub brush features a wooden ergonomic handle so you can comfortably and easily grip it while scrubbing. The natural wood is an ideal material for use with warm, soapy water and is easy to clean after use - just rinse it and leave it out to dry between uses.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ToolTtreaux Beauty Tools Nail Care Facial Care Cosmetic Tools (Many Styles)</h2>\n  <p>Keep your nails, lashes, eyebrows, and face looking clean, fresh, and groomed on the go with the ToolTreaux 9pc Deluxe Beauty Tool Kit! Our set comes with 9 basic tools every woman needs to be ready for any occasion on the go in one convenient set - an eyelash curler, eyebrow tweezer, nail brush, nail clippers, emery boards, and blackhead remover tools.</p>\n  <p>Our beauty scrub brush features a wooden ergonomic handle so you can comfortably and easily grip it while scrubbing. The natural wood is an ideal material for use with warm, soapy water and is easy to clean after use - just rinse it and leave it out to dry between uses.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>DUAL-SIDED NAIL BRUSH - Nail scrub brush features 2 different scrub sides, effective for removing dirt and particulates from hands and fingernails; Short bristles are ideal for scrubbing grime from underneath nails while longer bristles will gently massage and clean your fingers to keep your skin soft and supple; Safe for use on acrylic nails</li>\n    <li>DUAL-TIPPED EXTRACTOR TOOLS - Pore cleaner tool kit comes with 2 basic tools designed to remove blackheads easily; 1 tool includes a piercing needle and loop for safely puncturing and removing pimples &amp; 1 tool is designed for blemish and blackhead squeezing</li>\n    <li>3PC NAIL CLIPPER SET - Nail kit comes with a basic nail clipper and 2 emery board nail files to keep nails trimmed and groomed at home or on the go. Clipper features ultra-sharp blades to safely and easily cut nails without damaging your skin</li>\n    <li>2PC BASIC EYELASH TOOL KIT - ToolTreaux makeup tool kit comes with 2 professional tools for creating a natural, beautiful look; 1 premium eyelash curler and a set of eyebrow tweezers; Eyelash curler and tweezer are made of durable, high-quality corrosion-resistant stainless steel that won’t rust so you can count on them to last</li>\n    <li>PREMIUM DESIGN - Beauty tools are made of high-quality corrosion-resistant stainless steel that won’t rust so you can count on them to last; Nail files are made of flexible emery, essentially sandpaper that is safe for use on your body</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/71985/q3XlvwbHSs904flXZ8W4odAuYfqMKD-metaOXBjX2JlYXV0eV90b29sa2l0XzAxLmpwZw==-.jpg\" alt=\"Keep your nails, lashes, eyebrows, and face looking clean, fresh, and groomed on the go with the ToolTreaux 9pc Deluxe Beauty Tool Kit\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <p>Each brush features short bristles on one side and longer bristles on the other. Short bristles are ideal for scrubbing dirt from underneath your nails while the longer bristles will gently clean and massage your fingers to keep your skin soft and supple.</p>\n  <p>Although they may look intimidating, our blackhead removal tools are easy to use. Before you begin, make sure to clean your face with warm water to open pores and dry thoroughly. Sterilize your tools with hot soapy water or a preferred disinfectant before every use to ensure there is no bacteria or dirt. Proceed to pierce mature pimples and then choose the appropriate-sized loop to squeeze the acne out. Make sure to disinfect and dry your tools immediately after each use.</p>\n  <p>The nail clippers are made of durable, corrosion-resistant stainless steel that won’t rust so you can count on them for many uses. Each of the nail files is made of flexible emery that is essentially sandpaper designed to be safe for use on your body.</p>\n  <p>The included nail clippers feature an ergonomic handle to provide comfort and prevent slippage during use. They feature a chrome-polished sleek surface that is both simple yet fashionable, so they’ll easily fit with any of your other manicure tools.</p>\n  <p>Give your eyelashes and brows a natural, beautiful look with the ToolTreaux basic eye tool kit. This kit comes with one premium eyelash curler and tweezer to curl your eyelashes for a fuller look and to keep brows trimmed and shaped to your desired look.</p>\n  <p>The set weighs just .5 pounds and will easily fit inside just about any purse, bag, or beauty tool kit, making this a great makeup tool set for on-the-go use. Keep them inside of your purse or travel bag for quick touch-ups and hair removals if needed!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
